EXPRESSION: (CASE WHEN COALESCE(SFC_DQ_DATA_1_0.BIRTHDATE,'') IN ('',' ')  THEN DATE'1000-01-03' ELSE to_date(SFC_DQ_DATA_1_0.BIRTHDATE, 'yyyy-MM-dd') END )

(CASE  WHEN COALESCE(SFC_DQ_DATA_1_0.FAKE_CREATED_DATE,'') IN ('',' ') THEN CAST('1000-01-03 00:00:00' AS TIMESTAMP)  ELSE CAST(SUBSTR(SFC_DQ_DATA_1_0.FAKE_CREATED_DATE,1,10) || ' ' || SUBSTR(SFC_DQ_DATA_1_0.FAKE_CREATED_DATE,12,8) AS TIMESTAMP) END )
